name: Dark heart
description:
This painting has been generated by an AI, changing the style of the artist H. R. Giger with the realistic style of an unreal engine. You can see in the painting how mechanical tubes are connected to the heart, recreating Giger's characteristic Biomechanoid style.

Made with text-to-image synthesis (CLIP and VQGan).

By @HackNaut - 2021
